July 20, 2023 - Milly (stylized as MILLY) is an American fashion company. Specializing in women’s clothing, it was founded in 2000 by fashion designer Michelle Smith and Andrew Oshrin. The company is based in New York City and retails worldwide in department stores, via its own boutiques, its website and wholesales primarily to department stores.
